Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.50,0:00:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的舞臺是溫泉旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.20,0:00:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘溫泉的可怕傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露天溫泉中有事件的蛛絲馬跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.70,0:00:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.40,0:00:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是小孩 頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.10,0:00:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.30,0:02:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘溫泉雪夜振袖事件（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.70,0:02:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近肩酸還真是嚴重啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.00,0:02:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的溫泉 對治療肩酸可是非常的有效哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆先生 這是今晚的點心嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.20,0:03:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 那是客人委託我帶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.90,0:03:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是個很喜歡吃蛋糕的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.80,0:03:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說似乎是個有名的作家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你想吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.60,0:03:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.00,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨 恭候多時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.70,0:03:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很冷吧 好了 請進吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.20,0:03:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好漂亮的振袖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.20,0:03:32.80,zs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,20)}注:振袖是一種日本未婚女子穿的華麗長袖和服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庭院也好寬敞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人不是愛情小說家明智惠理小姐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.70,0:03:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.50,0:03:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非您就是名偵探毛利…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.90,0:03:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利小五郎先生嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.80,0:03:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.10,0:03:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是您吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.80,0:04:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.70,0:04:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在這種地方見到毛利先生真是太榮幸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.40,0:04:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是日賣電視臺的製作人 名叫阪東京一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.00,0:04:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站著說話也不太方便…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在舉行什麼聚會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.80,0:04:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這次是和大學館出版社的編輯一起邀請到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明智惠理老師來執筆編寫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.20,0:04:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計將于明年開始放映的新連續劇的劇本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續劇預計將描寫三個年輕的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.20,0:04:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及她們如何實現夢想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.40,0:04:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 特地採訪了活躍於各個領域的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.40,0:04:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 這次邀請了賴子女士母校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.50,0:04:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王道大學的三位女性畢業生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.40,0:04:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活躍於巴黎和紐約的時裝模特 柴崎明日香小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.70,0:04:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.20,0:05:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 這位是在東都藝術展上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.60,0:05:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得了最佳新人獎的油畫新秀 安西繪麻小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.40,0:05:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好 請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.50,0:05:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.90,0:05:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 接下來這位是目前在音樂界…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.00,0:05:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是流行樂作曲家 深津春美小姐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.60,0:05:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是您忠實的崇拜者啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.10,0:05:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.70,0:05:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就一支曲子走紅 還真受歡迎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.90,0:05:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後馬上就會消失吧 這樣的人可有很多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.10,0:05:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人三個樣 三位都是充滿個性又漂亮的美人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請走這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏也有很漂亮的振袖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.50,0:05:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 為什麼到處都裝飾著振袖和腰帶呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.00,0:05:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這附近祭祀著振袖之神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.40,0:06:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各家各戶都是這樣裝飾的 很尋常的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是振袖之神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.20,0:06:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明智老師的新作 真是令人期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫我惠理啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.30,0:06:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…  其實是因為和我媽媽的名字讀音相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.50,0:06:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫起“惠理老師”來 感覺有點怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.50,0:06:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然字寫出來不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.90,0:06:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 人家叫我明智老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.30,0:06:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺弄得像個偵探一樣  很不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.00,0:06:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說這附近祭祀著叫“振袖之神”的神明啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 不過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.30,0:06:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖之神也有被叫作“振袖般若”的可怕一面哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.80,0:06:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖般若
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.00,0:06:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自古流傳下來的民間傳說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古時候 這村子裏住著一位叫做阿花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.00,0:06:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心地善良的勤勞女子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.10,0:06:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某天 阿花救了一位扭傷了腳的武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.40,0:06:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為回禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.50,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她得到了很多漂亮的振袖和腰帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心懷嫉妒的村裏地主家的姐妹倆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.40,0:07:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誣陷阿花莫須有的罪名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.50,0:07:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫來了衙門裏的人 奪走了阿花的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.00,0:07:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿花行刑的當晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.00,0:07:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐妹倆展開到手的振袖和腰帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉浸在喜悅當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.30,0:07:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然間 燈一下子滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.40,0:07:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被慘叫聲所驚動 家裏人慌忙跑去一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.20,0:07:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋪著振袖的地板之上 妹妹已經斷氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.50,0:07:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也被許多腰帶纏住 溺死在院中的池塘裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了阿花怨念之深的村裏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.10,0:07:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設立了祠堂 作為村子的守護神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.10,0:07:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在各處 祭祀著振袖之神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.20,0:07:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 那裏就是被叫做“振袖之神的大社”的神社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您知道得還真詳細呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.40,0:07:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為要寫東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.50,0:07:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以經常呆在琴屋旅館收集資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是春美小姐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.60,0:08:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是她 春美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.90,0:08:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這棵樹叫振袖櫻 其樹齡有500年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.90,0:08:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一到春天 樹枝就會被盛開的櫻花所覆蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.90,0:08:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去簡直就像是一幅美麗的振袖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.00,0:08:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春美小姐你也對這村子很熟悉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.00,0:08:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 因為大學時的前輩很喜歡櫻花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾和我說過這棵樹的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.10,0:08:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起了這事 就到這裏來看看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.30,0:08:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個祠堂是做什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼你又到處亂竄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.90,0:08:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是參拜振袖的祠堂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.40,0:08:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參拜振袖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.10,0:08:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖之神 同時也是復仇之神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.40,0:08:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複 復仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.30,0:08:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說深夜裏穿上振袖前來參拜的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依靠自己的力量無法昭雪的仇恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.70,0:09:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖之神就會代替他去復仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.30,0:09:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面的千代紙人偶 是前來參拜振袖之神的人供奉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.30,0:09:12.00,zs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,20)}注:千代紙是日本的一種印花手工藝紙多用於做人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.60,0:09:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有新人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.10,0:09:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.60,0:09:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說有人最近參拜了振袖嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.00,0:09:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這意思是想要報復的人有兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是別人的惡作劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.10,0:09:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意 蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.50,0:09:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那不也是祠堂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.00,0:09:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠煩的 那肯定是客房嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.70,0:09:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏也祭祀著振袖之神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.80,0:09:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非 裏邊也有千代紙人偶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.60,0:09:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我有點擔心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.90,0:10:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 爸爸 去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.60,0:10:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.90,0:10:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 小蘭那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.80,0:10:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會有什麼紙人偶嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.70,0:10:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧 什麼也沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.90,0:10:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.20,0:10:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮  和宣傳手冊上畫的一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.40,0:10:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服極了 舒服極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.70,0:10:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服極了 舒服極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.30,0:10:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.50,0:10:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.90,0:10:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夥兒 能接受4天來的採訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.80,0:10:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人真是感激不盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.80,0:10:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠理小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.70,0:10:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓我在連續劇裏成為最搶眼的角色哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.70,0:11:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還沒決定故事怎樣展開呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.90,0:11:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要現在就拜託你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.40,0:11:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 阪東先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.80,0:11:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓春美小姐來寫主題曲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.80,0:11:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意 那就拜託您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.20,0:11:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能繼續大受歡迎就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.00,0:11:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.70,0:11:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是一開始就是空的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.60,0:11:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 再來一瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.50,0:11:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一瓶…只要一瓶就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.30,0:11:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我就不喝了 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.70,0:11:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不～行～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.80,0:11:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啊 柯南你好狡猾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.90,0:11:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 方便嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.00,0:12:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.60,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 我是想找毛利先生商量點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.30,0:12:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.20,0:12:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊 還以為出什麼事了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.20,0:12:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前在我大學三年級的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.90,0:12:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校園裏違禁藥物很流行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.40,0:12:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為進行秘密交易的販賣主謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.40,0:12:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個女學生被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.30,0:12:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她本人雖然否認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.10,0:12:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在她的櫃櫥裏發現了違禁藥物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.20,0:12:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後為了證明自己的清白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.50,0:12:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她從大學的建築物上縱身跳下死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的名字叫鈴鹿櫻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.20,0:12:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在振袖櫻樹下說很喜歡櫻花的很溫柔的那位前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.70,0:13:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的前輩會秘密販賣違禁藥物是根本不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.40,0:13:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次 再一次調查一下這件事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.70,0:13:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經都過了五年了啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.80,0:13:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實那時傳言說另有主謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.50,0:13:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那些學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.40,0:13:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些… 是有權勢人家的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.10,0:13:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校園裏也沒人敢說她們什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.70,0:13:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.20,0:13:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴崎明日香和安西繪麻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.70,0:13:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香是柴崎議員的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.00,0:13:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪麻是安西環球集團社長的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.90,0:13:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩人和正義感很強的櫻子經常起衝突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請毛利先生一定要幫這個忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.80,0:13:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 我一定會盡我所能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.40,0:13:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.50,0:13:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜歡那位前輩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.90,0:14:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候父母就去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叔父夫婦把我養大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.70,0:14:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻子的雙親也在火災中喪生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.70,0:14:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她對我非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.20,0:14:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生你們也去泡溫泉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.90,0:14:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠理老師也是去泡溫泉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 稍微有點冷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.30,0:14:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼等會兒我們去喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.40,0:14:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 工作還沒做完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.50,0:14:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那待會見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.70,0:14:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被人租下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.60,0:14:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了鎖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.20,0:14:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了 還有30分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.30,0:14:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上去打會兒乒乓球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.70,0:15:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.90,0:15:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁很熱鬧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.00,0:15:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭她們在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.10,0:15:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發球了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.30,0:15:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.40,0:15:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐已經洗好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.00,0:15:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還沒進去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.90,0:15:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經被人租下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.70,0:15:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深津小姐戴著眼鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了摘隱形眼鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.80,0:15:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛去摘掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經過了11點半了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包租11點就結束了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.50,0:15:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里 你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.90,0:15:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女溫泉浴池
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.40,0:16:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼還在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是打不開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才沒有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.20,0:16:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是覺得拿在手裏冷冷的 心裏發毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.10,0:16:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.80,0:16:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.20,0:16:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖般若
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.60,0:16:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 把門拿掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.40,0:16:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.90,0:16:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.40,0:16:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醉意全都沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.60,0:16:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 有人在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.00,0:16:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有是有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.70,0:17:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.50,0:17:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香小姐 振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.20,0:17:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 胸口被刺了一刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.40,0:17:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖般若的傳說… 難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.30,0:17:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中是姐妹兩人被殺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.20,0:17:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.80,0:17:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.20,0:17:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香小姐在露天溫泉裏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.70,0:17:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道被誰給殺害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.70,0:17:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.80,0:17:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪麻小姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.80,0:17:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.90,0:17:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個小時左右之前到對面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.80,0:17:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪麻小姐靴子的痕跡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.00,0:18:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在那裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.00,0:18:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 注意腳印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.10,0:18:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 你以為我是幹什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是振袖般若嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.30,0:18:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏也是胸口被刺了一刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面只有繪麻小姐的腳印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.50,0:18:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說這裏是被大雪封閉的密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.20,0:18:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要勞駕名偵探毛利先生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.80,0:18:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.50,0:18:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這個村的巡查小倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.30,0:18:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯繫縣警察局了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 已經聯繫過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.90,0:18:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為積雪要明天早晨才能到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早晨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.10,0:19:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們來搜查和保護現場了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.50,0:19:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店主 拿10張大一點的浴巾過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.60,0:19:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在廳裏等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.00,0:19:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢一點 小倉先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.30,0:19:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 輕輕地蓋著腳印… 慢一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.20,0:19:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要經過長廊下的道路就可以走到後門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這裏連一個腳印也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.60,0:19:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個… 什麼地方有點不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.60,0:19:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼 總覺得有點不對勁的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.00,0:19:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛 揭開的話腳印會被雪覆蓋掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在這裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.80,0:19:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 惠理老師說讓大家坐下來比較好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.20,0:19:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解到了什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.60,0:20:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賴子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.60,0:20:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪麻小姐經過大廳是10點半左右吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.90,0:20:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他什麼人經過嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 沒有其他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下可麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.70,0:20:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.50,0:20:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是繪麻小姐被殺的祠堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.50,0:20:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍的積雪上只有繪麻小姐本人的腳印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來繪麻小姐是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.20,0:20:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 現場沒有出現類似兇器一樣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.70,0:20:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.40,0:20:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其次是明日香小姐被殺的露天溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.10,0:20:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那裏去必須經過娛樂場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.30,0:20:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而10點半以後蘭和我們都在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.20,0:20:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人經過的話我們就會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.50,0:20:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是從山谷爬上懸崖進入的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.50,0:20:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查過了 懸崖上沒有可疑的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.60,0:21:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說來 明日香小姐有可能是10點半之前被殺的喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.50,0:21:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在露天溫泉池底發現了凶刀和電擊槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.90,0:21:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能犯人是用電擊槍把被害人擊暈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.80,0:21:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後實施犯罪的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.20,0:21:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶刀是刀柄處有貝殼裝飾的短刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.70,0:21:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向女老闆確認了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.90,0:21:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是院子裏祠堂中供奉的神刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.40,0:21:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.00,0:21:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外還有一件事 繪麻小姐的頭巾在露天溫泉被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.60,0:21:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭巾上沾有血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.70,0:21:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.90,0:21:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這就是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.30,0:21:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說她們兩人如果是被同一把短刀所殺害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.00,0:21:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼犯罪過程就是先加害繪麻小姐然後是明日香小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.80,0:21:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而從繪麻小姐在10點半之前還活著來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.50,0:21:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香小姐就是在那之後被殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.00,0:21:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是怎麼進入露天溫泉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.40,0:21:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庭院的祠堂周圍居然一個腳印也沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.40,0:22:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是幽靈 怎麼可能有這樣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.20,0:22:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是報應啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.60,0:22:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖般若的報應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.30,0:22:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.80,0:22:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.70,0:22:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在神社的祠堂裏供奉著兩個穿著振袖的人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.20,0:22:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖般若的詛咒把明日香和繪麻她們兩人給殺害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.90,0:22:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.50,0:22:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報應這樣的事絕對不會有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.80,0:22:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 犯人到底用了怎樣的手法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.20,0:24:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是參拜振袖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.90,0:24:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻子小姐用參拜振袖向兩人復仇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.20,0:24:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.10,0:24:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的 所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.80,0:24:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以前輩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.40,0:24:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 襪子全濕透了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.40,0:24:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 小蘭姐姐 等等嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.30,0:24:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.60,0:24:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘溫泉雪夜振袖事件（後篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.80,0:24:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.10,0:24:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.90,0:24:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐有腰帶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.60,0:24:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是空手道黑帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.00,0:24:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說那個啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.50,0:00:23.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日の舞台は温泉旅館！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.20,0:00:24.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘湯に伝わるコワ～イ伝説！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露天の湯から事件の匂い！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.70,0:00:28.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たった１つの真実見抜く
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.40,0:00:29.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見た目は子供 頭脳は大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.10,0:00:32.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その名は「名探偵コナン」！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.00,0:02:32.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.80,0:02:33.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,えっ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.90,0:02:49.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いや～最近肩凝りがひどくてね～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.80,0:02:53.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うちの温泉は肩凝りによく効きますよ。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほほう！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.00,0:02:58.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ！番頭さん　これ　今夜のデザート？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.30,0:03:02.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残念でした　お客さんの頼まれ物ですよ。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.90,0:03:04.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ケーキがお好きな人でねぇ。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.70,0:03:05.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いや　何でも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.50,0:03:08.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有名な作家先生らしいですよ。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.30,0:03:09.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふ～ん。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,コナンくん　食べたかったんでしょう？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.60,0:03:13.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,えっ！いや～えへへへへ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.80,0:03:23.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いらっしゃいませ　お待ち申しておりました。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.50,0:03:26.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お寒かったでしょう　さぁ　中へ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.20,0:03:32.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うわ～　キレイな振袖！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お庭も広い！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.20,0:03:41.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あれ？あの人　恋愛小説家の明智恵理さんじゃ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おおっ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああっ！イテテ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.70,0:03:45.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お父さん…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.50,0:03:47.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ん？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.80,0:03:49.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.40,0:03:52.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もしかして　名探偵の毛利…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利小五郎さんじゃありませんか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.40,0:03:55.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おっ？毛利…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうですよね？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.30,0:04:02.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あ…はい　そうですが…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.10,0:04:04.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いや～こんなところで
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.30,0:04:12.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私「日売りテレビ」のプロデューサー阪東京一と申します
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.20,0:04:14.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああ…　そう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.50,0:04:07.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利さんと　お会いできるなんて光栄です
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.20,0:04:13.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.70,0:04:16.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まぁ　立ち話もなんですから…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.60,0:04:17.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.80,0:04:19.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.60,0:04:23.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…で　これは　何の集まりですかな？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.80,0:04:27.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,実はこちらの「大学館出版」さんとうちとで
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.70,0:04:32.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来春放送の新作ドラマをあちらの明智恵理先生に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.10,0:04:34.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執筆していただくことになったんです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.40,0:04:38.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ドラマは3人の若い女性達が
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.20,0:04:41.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢をかなえて行く姿を描く予定なんです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.40,0:04:45.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それで　各方面で活躍中の女性を取材してまして…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.20,0:04:52.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…で　今回は　頼子さんの母校王道大学の卒業生3人に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集まっていただいたんです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.30,0:04:56.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,パリやニューヨークで活躍中の
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ファッションモデル柴崎明日香さん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.70,0:04:59.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.70,0:05:02.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おおっ！ビューチフル！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…で　こちらが
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.40,0:05:08.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東都芸術展で新人賞を受賞された油絵画家　安西絵麻さん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.30,0:05:09.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうぞよろしく
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ワッハッハ！チャーミング！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.90,0:05:14.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…で続いて　今　音楽業界で…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.90,0:05:18.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,シンガーソングライターの深津はるみさんですよね！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.50,0:05:20.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私　大ファンなんです！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.30,0:05:23.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,えっ？あ…ありがとう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.80,0:05:27.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あら　1曲ヒットしたぐらいでずいぶん人気者なのね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.00,0:05:31.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,す～ぐ消えちゃったりして多いらしいわよ　そんな人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.30,0:05:40.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いや～三者三様！3人とも個性的で　お美しいですな～！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はぁ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.10,0:05:43.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こちらです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.50,0:05:48.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うわ～ここにもキレイな振袖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.60,0:05:53.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの～あちこちに振袖や帯が飾られてますけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.60,0:05:55.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうしてなんですか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.20,0:05:58.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この辺りは振袖様をお祭りしてて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.50,0:06:03.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どの家庭もこのように飾るのですよ　ごく普通に…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.30,0:06:06.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,へぇ…振袖様ですか…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.20,0:06:11.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明智先生の新作　今から楽しみです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恵理って呼んでください
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.20,0:06:19.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でも…実は母も同じ名前で　恵理先生って呼ぶのって
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.10,0:06:22.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何か　変な感じで…あの…字は違うんですけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.90,0:06:26.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私だって明智先生なんて呼ばれるのは
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何だか探偵みたいで恥ずかしいわ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.00,0:06:35.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この辺りは振袖様っていう神様をお祭りしているんですってね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.60,0:06:38.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ええ　でもね　振袖様には
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.40,0:06:41.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖般若っていう恐ろしい顔もあるのよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖般若？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.10,0:06:46.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古くから伝わる民話よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.50,0:06:52.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昔　この村に　お花という働き者で心優しい娘がおりました
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.00,0:06:57.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ある日お花は足を滑らせケガをしたお侍を助け
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.70,0:07:01.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お礼に美しい振袖や帯をたくさんいただきました
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.30,0:07:07.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それをねたんだ　庄屋の娘2人はお花に　あらぬ濡れ衣を着せ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.50,0:07:10.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,役人に引渡し着物を奪ってしまったのです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.90,0:07:16.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お花が処刑された夜　姉妹は手に入れた振袖や帯を広げ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜びに浸っていました
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すると突然フッと明かりが消え…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（キャ～）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.30,0:07:27.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲鳴に驚き家のものが慌てて駆けつけると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.20,0:07:32.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床一面に広がった振袖の上で妹が息絶え
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.50,0:07:36.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姉は　庭の池で何本もの帯びに絡みつかれ　おぼれていました
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お花の怨念の深さを知った村人達は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.10,0:07:44.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祠を建てて　村の守り神として
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.20,0:07:47.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いたる所で振袖様をお祭りしているのです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.10,0:07:52.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そして　あれが「振袖様の大社」と呼ばれている社よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,よくご存知なんですねぇ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.50,0:07:59.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あら  執筆で時々「琴屋旅館」にこもってるから…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.40,0:08:04.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ！あれ…はるみさんじゃない？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.70,0:08:06.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当だ！はるみさん！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.90,0:08:13.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この木は振袖桜といって樹齢500年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.80,0:08:17.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春になれば大きく広がった枝が満開の花に覆われ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.30,0:08:21.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まるで美しい振袖のように見えるんですよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.00,0:08:24.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はるみさんもこの村には詳しいんですか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.50,0:08:29.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,えっ？いえ！大学の先輩がとても桜が好きで
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.50,0:08:32.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この木のことも話してくれたことがあったんです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.10,0:08:35.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それを思い出して来てみたの…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.60,0:08:41.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ！ねぇねぇ　蘭ねえちゃんあの祠何だろう？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,えっ？ああ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.10,0:08:45.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こら！ガキはチョロチョロと…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは振袖参りの祠よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.50,0:08:49.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,えっ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.20,0:08:50.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖参り…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.00,0:08:54.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖様は復讐の神様でもあるの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復讐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深夜振袖をかぶってお参りすると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自分の力では晴らせない恨みを
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.90,0:09:05.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖様が変わって晴らしてくれるという言い伝えがあるの…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.20,0:09:11.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中の千代紙人形は振袖参りをした人達が奉納したものよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.00,0:09:15.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ！新しい人形があるわ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.10,0:09:17.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しがも2つ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何だって！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.20,0:09:19.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.60,0:09:24.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かが最近振袖参りの願をかけたってことか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.90,0:09:28.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨みを晴らしたい相手が2人いるということです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.40,0:09:28.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.30,0:09:35.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうせ誰かのいたずらだ…気にすんな蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.70,0:09:36.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,えっ　うん…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.50,0:09:39.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ　あれも祠じゃない？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.00,0:09:40.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,えっ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うるせぇな～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.40,0:09:44.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客室の決まってるんだろ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あそこも振袖様を祭ってるんです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.20,0:09:51.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まさか…あの中にも千代紙人形が…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.70,0:09:55.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,んなわけねえだろう　ハハハハハ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.70,0:10:00.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ…でも何か気になるから　お願いお父さん確かめてきてよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,えっ　俺が？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.90,0:10:09.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…ったく　もう　蘭のヤツ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.70,0:10:12.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紙人形なんかあるわけないっつうのに…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.80,0:10:15.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほれなぁ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だね…何にもないよ～！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.90,0:10:20.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう　よかったわ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おおっ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.10,0:10:29.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すっご～い！パンフレットと同じ！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.50,0:10:35.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いや～極楽！極楽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.70,0:10:39.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極楽極楽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.40,0:10:42.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わ～キレイ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.60,0:10:45.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.80,0:10:49.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆さん  4日間の取材にお付き合いいただき
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.10,0:10:52.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当にありがとうございました
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.70,0:10:55.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恵理さんドラマでは私がモデルの役を
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一番目立たせてよね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.80,0:11:01.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まだどんなストーリーになるかも決まってないのよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから　今から頼んでるんじゃん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.40,0:11:07.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうだ　阪東さん！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.80,0:11:10.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はるみさんに主題歌歌っていただきましょうよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.90,0:11:11.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,えっ？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.80,0:11:15.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おおっ！そりゃいい！ぜひ　お願いしますよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.20,0:11:19.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それまで人気が続いてればいいけど…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おいしいね　コナンくん！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.80,0:11:25.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うん！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.30,0:11:32.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,う～ん…あれれ？はじめからカラだったんじゃないのかな～？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.70,0:11:34.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,んなわけねえだろ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.70,0:11:37.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭ちゃん　へへ…追加を…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.50,0:11:43.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ん～じゃあ　あと1本だけ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.30,0:11:47.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ　それで終わりにすっから～蘭ちゃ～ん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.70,0:11:49.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ダ～メ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.80,0:11:54.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やだ～コナンくんズルい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの～ちょっといいですか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はい　どうぞ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.50,0:12:01.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あら　はるみさん！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.60,0:12:05.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,実は毛利さんにご相談したいことが…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.90,0:12:07.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お父さん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.20,0:12:09.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はひ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.30,0:12:10.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お父さん！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.20,0:12:12.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相談？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.10,0:12:18.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あ…な～んらふぁれかとおもったら…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.20,0:12:26.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5年前…私が大学3年生の頃です…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.90,0:12:32.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キャンパスで違法な薬物が流行り密売の首謀者として
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.30,0:12:34.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ある女子学生が浮かびました…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.20,0:12:36.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人は否定しましたが
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.10,0:12:40.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼女のロッカーから薬物が発見されたんです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.20,0:12:43.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そして無実を訴え
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.60,0:12:47.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学の建物から身を投げて命を絶ちました…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.20,0:12:47.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おっ？！          えっ？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.00,0:12:50.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その人の名は鈴鹿桜子さん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.10,0:12:56.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖桜の下で話した桜が大好きだった優しい先輩です
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.60,0:12:59.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな先輩が薬物密売なんて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.10,0:13:01.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんなことをするはずがありません！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利さんお願いです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.40,0:13:07.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう一度…もう一度この事件を調べなおしてください！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.10,0:13:08.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,う～ん…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.70,0:13:12.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5年も前となるとねぇ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.90,0:13:17.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,実は当時　首謀者は他にいるといううわさがあったんです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.30,0:13:17.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,えっ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.30,0:13:22.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しかし　その学生は　その…有力者の娘で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.30,0:13:26.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学内でも　彼女達に口出しできる者はいなくて…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.00,0:13:28.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼女達？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.10,0:13:32.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴崎明日香さんと安西絵麻さんです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.60,0:13:35.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香さんは柴崎代議士の娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.10,0:13:40.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絵麻さんはゼネコン「安西グローバル」の社長の娘なんです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.90,0:13:45.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2人は正義感の強い桜子さんとぶつかることが多かったんです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうか毛利さん！お願いします！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.60,0:13:48.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うん…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.70,0:13:53.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分かりました　できる限りのことはやってみましょう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ　ありがとうございます！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.60,0:13:59.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その先輩のこと大好きだったんですね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.00,0:14:05.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私　幼い頃　父と母を亡くし叔父夫婦に育てられたんです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.80,0:14:09.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桜子さんも火事で両親を亡くしていたので
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.00,0:14:12.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,とても親切にしてもらったんです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.40,0:14:28.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あら？毛利さん達もお風呂ですか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恵理先生もお風呂だったんですか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.00,0:14:33.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ええ…ちょっと冷えちゃって！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.50,0:14:36.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だったらどうです？後で１杯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.30,0:14:40.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ごめんなさい　まだ仕事が残ってますんで
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.40,0:14:42.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあ　後でね！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.10,0:14:47.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あれ？貸切になってる！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.00,0:14:48.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当だ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.70,0:14:54.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍵が掛かってるわ！仕方ないわね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.70,0:14:58.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あと30分ですから　上で卓球でもやってましょうか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.60,0:14:59.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうですね！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.80,0:15:07.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隣はずいぶん賑やかだな…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.00,0:15:10.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭達　何やってんだ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行くわよ～！えいっ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.20,0:15:15.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,よ～し　それっ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.40,0:15:16.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああっ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.30,0:15:20.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ！あれ？蘭姉ちゃん達もう上がってたの？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.10,0:15:25.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ううん！まだ入ってないの　貸切になってたから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.70,0:15:26.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふ～ん…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.60,0:15:30.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あれ？はるみさん　メガネ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.80,0:15:34.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,コンタクト外すの忘れてて　さっき外してきたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.40,0:15:40.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,う～ん…グ～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.60,0:15:45.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう11時半　回ったわ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.10,0:15:48.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貸切は11時まででしたよね？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ええ  行きましょうか！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.70,0:15:53.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふえっ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ど…どこに行くんだ？みんな
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.00,0:15:57.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女湯！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,な…何！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あら？まだ入ってるわ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.20,0:16:05.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やっぱり開かない！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.40,0:16:08.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ん？何かしら？これ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.50,0:16:10.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あら？さっきはなかったわよ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.10,0:16:16.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何かひんやり冷たくて気持悪い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.90,0:16:21.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ！！何これ？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.00,0:16:21.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.70,0:16:22.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうした？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.20,0:16:24.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖般若
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.90,0:16:31.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ！おじさん！この戸を外して！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.70,0:16:34.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お…おう！！どいてろ～！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.30,0:16:39.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うが～！ん～！！うお～！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.00,0:16:39.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.30,0:16:42.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うっお…　おっとっと！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.80,0:16:45.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お父さん？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.30,0:16:48.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,アハ…酔いが　すっ飛んじまったぜ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.50,0:16:51.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,コナンくん！誰かいるの？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.50,0:16:43.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,イテ～！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いるにはいるけど…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.70,0:17:01.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香さん？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.70,0:17:02.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キャ～！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.50,0:17:05.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香君！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香君　しっかりしろ！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.90,0:17:12.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああ…ダメだ！胸をひと突きだ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.30,0:17:16.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖般若の伝説…まさか！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.70,0:17:17.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ  コナンくんどこ行くの？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.20,0:17:22.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伝説では姉妹が殺害されている！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.20,0:17:29.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あら？どうしたの？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.80,0:17:30.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香さんが…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一体何事です？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.30,0:17:35.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香さんが露天風呂で！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何者かに殺害されてます！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.30,0:17:39.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,えっ？                な…何ですって？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.90,0:17:40.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絵麻さんは？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.70,0:17:45.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そ…そういえば1時間ぐらい前に向こうへ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ！絵麻さんのブーツの跡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.00,0:18:01.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あそこか？彼女は！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.00,0:18:04.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おじさん　足跡に気をつけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.30,0:18:07.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分かってる！俺の職業　何だと思ってる！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.30,0:18:20.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.70,0:18:25.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やはり　振袖般若か…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.10,0:18:28.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こっちも胸をひと突きだ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外には絵麻さんのブーツの足跡以外なかった…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.60,0:18:36.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,つまりここは雪に閉ざされた密室…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼しまっす！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.10,0:18:43.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名探偵の毛利さんとお見受けしまっす！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.50,0:18:44.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああ…そうですが…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.80,0:18:48.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はっ　本官はこの村の駐在小倉巡査であります！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.20,0:18:50.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,県警には？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はっ！連絡しました
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.80,0:18:55.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…がな～んせ　この積雪でがんすから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.00,0:18:57.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到着は明け方になるかと…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明け方か…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.80,0:19:03.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しょうがねえな…俺達で現場検証と保存をやっとくか…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.60,0:19:08.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女将さん！バスタオルを10枚ほど持ってきてください
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.80,0:19:10.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あ…はい！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.50,0:19:14.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆さんは広間で待機しててください
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はい！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.90,0:19:17.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ゆっくりね　小倉さん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.20,0:19:21.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうそう…そ～っとかぶせて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.80,0:19:24.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ブーツの足跡を…ゆっくりね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.20,0:19:29.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この軒下の道を通れば裏口に行くことができる…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しかし　足跡ひとつないな…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.60,0:19:39.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あれ？何か変だ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.60,0:19:44.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何だ…何か引っかかる…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.00,0:19:48.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こら！めくったら足跡に雪が積もっちまうだろう！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　こちらでしたか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.70,0:19:56.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,イスのほうが楽だろうからって恵理先生が…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.20,0:19:58.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何か分かりましたか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.10,0:19:59.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,う～ん…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.50,0:20:03.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頼子さん　絵麻さんがこのロビーを通ったのは
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10時半頃でしたね？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はい！そうですけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他に誰か通りましたか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いえ誰も…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.50,0:20:12.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,う～ん…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.00,0:20:15.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厄介でねえかな～こりゃあ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.70,0:20:17.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ど…どういうことなんです？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.50,0:20:22.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まず絵麻さんが殺害された祠ですが
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.50,0:20:24.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周囲に降り積もった雪には
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.70,0:20:27.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絵麻さんのブーツの跡以外ありませんでした
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.90,0:20:29.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それじゃぁ絵麻さんは自殺？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.30,0:20:30.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いいえ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.70,0:20:34.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場からは凶器らしき物は出て来なかったが…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.90,0:20:35.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.30,0:20:39.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次に　明日香さんが殺害された露天風呂ですが
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.10,0:20:43.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あそこへ行くには遊技場を通らなければ行けません
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.30,0:20:48.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そこには10時半以降蘭や私達がいましたから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.30,0:20:50.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他の者が通れば分かりますし…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.60,0:20:53.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷から崖を登って侵入するのは？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.50,0:20:57.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調べましたが崖に不審な痕跡はありませんでした
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.80,0:20:59.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それじゃあ　明日香さんは
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.50,0:21:01.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10時半より前に殺害されたんじゃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.40,0:21:06.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風呂の底から凶器の刃物とスタンガンが発見されました
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.00,0:21:10.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おそらく　犯人は被害者をスタンガンで気絶させ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.00,0:21:12.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯行に及んだのでしょう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.20,0:21:16.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刃物は柄に螺鈿細工のある短刀です
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.70,0:21:18.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女将に確認したところ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.90,0:21:21.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庭の祠に祭ってあるご神刀だそうです
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.40,0:21:23.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ご神刀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.00,0:21:28.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう１つ…絵麻さんのバンダナも露天風呂から発見されました
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.00,0:21:31.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バンダナには血が染みていました…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.70,0:21:32.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どういうこと？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.00,0:21:35.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは…つまり…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.30,0:21:39.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,つまり　2人が同一の短刀で殺害されたとすれば
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.10,0:21:44.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯行は絵麻さん　明日香さんの順に行われたことになります
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.70,0:21:48.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そして　絵麻さんは10時半まで生きていたわけですから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.60,0:21:51.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香さん殺害はそれ以降となります
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.10,0:21:54.80,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人はどうやって露天風呂へ行ったの？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.30,0:21:58.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庭の祠だって周りに足跡ひとつないなんて…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.30,0:22:03.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽霊じゃあるまいし　そんなことできるわけが…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.30,0:22:04.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祟りよ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.00,0:22:04.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,えっ？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.60,0:22:07.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖般若の祟りよ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.70,0:22:09.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,な…何をバカな！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.80,0:22:11.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私達　見たのよ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.70,0:22:16.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社の祠に振袖参りの人形が2つ奉納されてたのを！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.20,0:22:20.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖般若が明日香と絵麻2人を呪い殺したのよ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.30,0:22:22.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんなこと…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.50,0:22:26.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな祟りなんてことあるはずがない！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.80,0:22:31.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しかし　犯人は一体どんなトリックを使ったんだ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.10,0:24:01.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖参りよ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.80,0:24:05.30,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桜子さんが振袖参りで2人に復讐したのよ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.50,0:24:06.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああっ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.20,0:24:08.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そういうことか！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.10,0:24:14.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうです…だから…だから先輩は…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.10,0:24:15.60,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.40,0:24:20.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちょっと～　靴下がびしょ濡れじゃない！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.00,0:24:23.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あっ　ちょっと！　蘭ねえちゃん　待ってよ～！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.30,0:24:25.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.60,0:24:28.70,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘湯雪闇振袖事件（後編） 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.80,0:24:47.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT! 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.10,0:24:49.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.90,0:24:51.50,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭ねぇちゃんは帯持ってる？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.60,0:24:52.90,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黒帯ならね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.00,0:24:54.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あぁ、それじゃなくって…
